    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 8pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Times New Roman';}\n.html-preview .customClass1 {font-family: 'Times New Roman';}\n.html-preview .customClass3 {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .customClass30 {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .consplusnonformat {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 761px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 93px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 34px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 105px}</style><p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#2}Даъво аризаси берилаётган суднинг номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\"> га </span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">Даъвогар: </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#5}Даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О си</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#6}Даъвогарнинг юридик манзили</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#7}Даъвогарнинг СТИР рақами</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#8}Даъвогарнинг телефон рақами</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#9}Даъвогарнинг электрон манзили</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">Жавобгар: </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#10}Жавобгарнинг Ф.И.О си</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#11}Жавобгарнинг юридик манзили</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#12}Жавобгарнинг СТИР рақами</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#13}Жавобгарнинг телефон рақами</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-bottom: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">ДАЪВО АРИЗА</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">(Маҳсулот камомади қийматини ундириш тўғрисида</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">«юки текшириб берилган ҳамда темирйўл орқали юборилган ҳолларда»)</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 29.333333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Бизнинг манзилимизга <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#15}Темирйўл варақасининг рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> рақамли темир йўл варақаси орқали </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Маҳсулот етказиб берилган вагон рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> -сонли вагонда келган юкни темир йўл ходимлари томонидан текшириб топшириш вақтида юк сақланмаган ҳолатда ва </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Аниқланган камомад миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> камомад билан келганлиги аниқланди ва улар </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Тижорат далолатномаси тузилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> да тузилган, </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Тижорат далолатномаси сони</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-сонли тижорат далолатномаси ва умумий шаклдаги далолатномалар билан тасдиқланган.</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Маҳсулот қиймати даъвогар томондан </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#20}Даъвогар томонидан тўлов амалга оширилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> да </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Тўлов топшириғи рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">рақамли тўлов топшириғи орқали тўланган.</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ҳисобга асосан камомад қиймати </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#22}Умумий камомад миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">сўмни ташкил қилади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 26.666666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Бизнинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#23}Даъвогар томонидан талабнома юборилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да юборган талабномамизни жавобгар (жавобсиз қолдирди) асоссиз қаноатлантирмади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Юқоридагиларга ҳамда Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 437-456-моддалари, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Иқтисодий процессуал кодексининг 148, 149 ва 151-моддаларига асосан </span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28px;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">СЎРАЙМАН</span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 26.666666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"customClass1\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Юқоридагиларга асосан жавобгардан бизнинг фойдамизга </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#22}Умумий камомад миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">сўм камомад қийматини ундириб беришингизни сўраймиз.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"consplusnonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0.75pt; margin-bottom: 0.75pt;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Илова: </span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">{#24}Даъво аризага илова қилинаётган ҳужжатлар рўйхати</span></p>\n<p class=\"consplusnonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 0.75pt; margin-bottom: 0.75pt;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">Даъвогар:</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">{#5}Даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О си</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> ______________</span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-style: italic;\"> (имзо)</span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" margin-top: 0.75pt; margin-bottom: 0.75pt;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" margin-top: 0.75pt; margin-bottom: 0.75pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #000000;\">{#3}Даъво ариза берилган сана</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"customClass30\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
